column8: Review (after 06/19/2017, fragrances and gift sets only + DK deo)
Great smell This is very nice cologne for men. Has a great scent
Best Gift ever. I gave this to a male friend of mine for Father's Day and he was super surprised. He loved it and it came with a bonus of toiletry carrier. Good deal.
Love it! It's my favorite fragrance!

I would buy this product again without hesitation. Got this with one of my online shipments as a sampler. I then went on to buy the rollerball. Now for my birthday one of the engineers on my ship gave me a card with money in it and I went and purchased the bottle. Love this!!!!
Great fragrance. Beautiful fragranc! Love they way it smells on me and it's not over powering.

THIS ONE IS A REAL WINNER I love the DKNY fragrances, but had not tried this one. With the positive reviews and discounted price, I took a chance. Came the other day, and with one spray I knew I loved this particular fragrance. OMG, now I have three of her fragrances to love!!! Thanks so much DKNY.
Yaaas All of DKNY are great, as everyone knows! This one is light and sugary and green apply, terrific for summer!
the best! his is my go out, perfect for all seasons. love love

Great summer scent This reminds me of my happy days and teen years. This perfume is beautiful, young but mire sophisticated than other apple scents. This is going to be my daytime summer fragrance. I am amazed how long this lasted! It is fresh and I feel and smell so clean when I have this on!
Still love my Be Delicious This is my go to DKNY perfume, its delicate and feminine. It doesnt mess with my allergies and my husband loves it. It'sstaying power is great.
Very nice perfume. My husband bought this for me and I absolutely love the way it smells and so does he!
The only perfume I purchase. A couple sprays on my stomach & rubbing on my wrists and I don't smell it but I get compliments all day.
Love it! Fresh. Love to use it daily
Yum. This is wonderful smelling and the packaging is pretty enough to make you happy!
Scrumptious scent. This fragrance smells, quite simply, delicious. Very nice.
Don't like this one at all. I LOVE DKNY so I thought I would give this a try. It's not for me, its too woodsy not very feminine like my favorite-Be Delicious. I will be sending this one back.
Love DK. I love DK products, this fragrance is a light wonderful scent that I have enjoyed wearing. I will purchase this again.
Exellent. I really recommend this product, I love the smell, long lasting
Sexy and flirty This scent can be described as having 'sexy honey' scent. Not sweet and flowery but very alluring. My new favorite
Love it! It's amazing, but not overpowering!
I bought this for the convenience but it's not convenient if it doesn't last.

Love this travel sized enticing fragrance. Using my coconut body wash and body butter I still needed something to lift the one note of that fragrance on my skin and this is it. I always find one fragrance that means summer to me but buy it in a smaller size - and travel tubes are perfect - to see if it will be my "smell of the summer". DKNY is that and more. It's the fragrance you smell with wood notes that so complements my coconut base that it makes a new fragrance that has people in elevators asking me what I am wearing - in a good way - not that girl who sprayed who knows what and everyone is getting out on the next floor.... Dewy, woody, but with a floral lightness makes this my summertime jam.
Smells amazing! I love the smell of this perfume! I wear it all the time!
Great product!!! Use this product day or night.

Very nice! I was surprised how light and fresh this scent is. Usually DKNY fragrances are a little heavier but this one is nice and light, not too flowery. I just so wish these rollerball fragrances lasted a little longer. But I'll still buy them, much easier to have in my purse.
Fresh sweet fragrance. Love the roller ball application and am crazy about this scent.
good perfume. Good perfume smells good is soft and not like others that annoy the smell jijijiji
Fabulous Scent. Convenient and easy to transport.
Best produce ever. Great produce, I will buy again in the future!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Mesmerizingly heavenly. I have always been intrigued by Donna Karan since a young 20 year old. As I was going through fragrances I like to see new fragrances. A sales lady walked up to spray on some perfume SHE recommended. I sprayed on Donna Karan Cashmere Aura. I didn'the like it. As I approached Juniors there was a wonderful fragrance in the air near me. As I said something smells so good. I smelled my arm my heavenly scent. Light and capturing. I made a uturn went back to counter and purchased a travelers bottle. As I love it now. I went back to purchase a 3.4 only to find all stores had sent it back. I just ordered an available gift box from Macy's. This is my coping mega ism. So happy....
It's smell so good my husband love the smell, it's. It's smell so good my husband love the smell, it's last long I loved it I recommend this product.
Great deoderant. Love the subtle smell. I don't mind spending more for this have-to-have.
LOVE this deodorant. have searched for years and have never found one so great

love this stuff- the only deodorant I wear. Although it's pricey for a deodorant, I love the smell and it keeps my armpits dry. Make sure not to apply too heavy handed because it does go on white and can easily get on dark clothes. But the great perfume smell is worth it, as it lasts all day.

Pricey, but works perfectly. I have an issue with body odor - not even with perspiration itself, but that if wrong deodorant or no deodorant is chosen, my clothes will start smelling pretty soon, even if there is no visible perspiration marks. I bought this one accidentally and I am very happy, as the smell is weaker than some natural deodorants, it applies very softly and while pricey, works perfectly and lasts quite a while.
Expensive but worth it! It's the only thing I've found where I can be in surgery (work) and not pit out.
Love love love. This is the best, I've tried so many and this is my go to! If you have probable with sweating or just the smell of the deodorant not staying this is the one! Life changing.

I will over ever use this deodorant. Love love love. This last FOREVER. Ive always disliked using drug store deodorants. I wanted to use a higher end deodorant and this one is perfect. My last deodorant would break and sometimes sweat would drip down my arms (i know, yuck!) i dont have that problem with this.

The best. I have been using Cashmere deodorant for the last couple of years. I love everything about it. It goes on easy, last a long time, And smells great.
It helps that Cashmere Mist is my favorite fragrance.
It is pricey but a lot goes a long way with this deodorant.

not working very well. I saw this with many good reviews so I gave it a try. However, it does not work that well. It has nice smell from the beginning but quickly turns bad (especially in hot weather). It does not keep you dry. It is not recommended if you are going to where black outfits.

So Glad I Tried
I agree with all of the other 5 star reviews if you have tried it, you will not change.

Velvety good! I love, love, this deodorant by D.K. It's velvety soft against your skin. It has a soft scent. It even lightened my skin some. No more embarrassing darkened skin for me and no more yellow stains on clothing! Like what those other drug store kind do. Thank you D.K.!

Pure Gold!
Bought this on the recommendation of a friend and couldn't be more pleased with the results. This holds up after strenuous gym workouts and stays with me during my long days at work- I still feel and smell fresh!

The BEST Deodorant Ever!
OMG, I love this deodorant which has been my go-to for 3 years now! I refuse to go back to a drug-store brand. A little goes a long way; in fact, one bottle usually lasts me 8+ months

BEST
Best on the market ! Nordstrom is the best place to shop.
Men Love This One Ladies! Feminine, soft, powdery, light. I get compliments almost every time I wear this one, especially from men. Every woman should own a bottle of this classic!
My favorite. This has been my go to fragrance for many years

love it. 
just loving it and the price was great for me. Thanks
Men Love This One Ladies! Feminine, soft, powdery, light. I get compliments almost every time I wear this one, especially from men. Every woman should own a bottle of this classic!
Men Love This One Ladies! Feminine, soft, powdery, light. I get compliments almost every time I wear this one, especially from men. Every woman should own a bottle of this classic!

Men Love This One! I've owned 30 different fragrances in my years of perfume collecting, this was one of the very first. Out of all of them, this is the one I get the most compliments on. Especially men! My man, strangers, friends. It's the most feminine, soft, powdery, warm fragrance. A timeless classic! Every woman should own a bottle of Cashmere Mist <3
Wonderful scent. I love this scent - so light and fresh. I've worn it for years and never tire of it.
Only one I buy. I have used this since it came out the best

Oh..DK!! Just love this fragrance from DK!! Smells so elegant. It's one of my favorite perfumes. I always receive compliments when I wear it. Love that it's small enough to put into my purse and carry around.
Yes! I love it. I love the rollerball application. Sprays are sometimes difficult to control, this goes exactly where and in the amount you want.

My all time favorite. I use it daily as it is my favorite fragrance of all time... it's long lasting, aromatic and refreshing. To some it's expensive but I've been using for over ten years so I would definitely invest in it.
Smells Heavenly. Bought this for a gift but had a hard time parting with it. Waiting for another sale so I can gift that one.
Good price. I got this perfume on a very good deal so bought 5 if these 1 for me and 4 as gifts. The fragrance is OK. It does stay long. I cannot complain for the deal I got.. overall happy with it!
great purchase. my girlfriend loves the smell of karan aqua marine scent so much she is going into Macys to try other Donna Karan perfume scents.she also love the bag that came with the purchase.
Great Price. I love the fresh scent of this perfume and the price is worth it.
Donna Karan parfume spray. I love the fresh smell. A good purchase but. I love all of Donna Karan purgume
Lovely fragrance. I love this lovely soft summer fragrance. Would definitely be adding to my list of favorites.
Love it!! Charming fragrance!!! The combination of blooming florals and rich woods makes it a sensational fragrance. Great for an intimate evening, out with the girls, or to the clubs!!! Great buy!!!
Fantastic fragrance. I absolutely love how this fragrance smells on my skin, and it lasts for hours. Macy's has the best deals on fragrance from time to time.
Love it!! I love this fragrance. It is light and fresh. This is my first time using Aqua. I am very pleased with it.
Yummy and light Fragrance. I'm a Donna Karan fan all the way. When I smelled this fragrance, I had to have it in my collection of Donna Karan perfumes. Try it, I'm sure you'll like it!

I'll buy more when I run low. It has a nice, soft smell that is great for any use. Good for work, because it isn't too overbearing on your nose. Its also great for a classy casual night out. If you like Victorias Secret Intense, youll like this and vice versa. Although Intense has a more berry scent, and better for daytime.

Love this perfume! My husband picked me out this perfume for a gift and I have to say he did an amazing job. I receive compliments throughout the day and when I get a hug by my daughter at the end of the day and she tells me how good I smell I know this perfume will have a permanent spot in my collection.
Wow! Would have bought it at full price but got 50% off!! Bought the last 2 on the shelf!!

Smells good!!! Nice summer and date fragrance, lots of compliments and projection is better than expected.

Love this I bought this because it was a one day sale and thought of my bf didn't like it he could take it back. Turns out we both love it! Great smell. Stays on all day. Glad I ran across it. Would pay full price and recommend to anyone!
AWESOME PURCHASE!!!!!! I wore this to work and can you say "mesmerized". There were so many wonderful compliments, this just may be my new signature fragrance.
Deal I got this on in a deal price too but must say it turned out to be one of the best buys I have ever got online! I love the fragrance!
Love this Perfume. This smells so good and it last. Just brought this set yesterday and love it!
Amazing. Not to strong of a smell it's just right to get the heads turning
Smells Good It very convenient for travel.. I love it.. it smells very nice... a light scent.

great gift option bought it to give as a birthday gift, my friend was very happy !
;-)
A must have! Love this lip and perfume combo. Great for travel and a small clutch. Always getting compliments on it!

Nothing to write home about. I'm somewhat disappointed in this fragrance. It is nowhere near as good as the Michael Kors original fragrance for men. A much better choice would be Chrome by Azzaro. Won't be buying this again.
The best purchase Ever Thank You. Is a very good product ever Purchase in my Life And will be do again I hope I find the same Product next time.
nan jack. I bought last week this locion for the men. I loved
Best product. MK Jasmine is one of the best fragrances in my experience. I would have liked it in Gift pack as it used to be in the past with body lotion and roll-on
Love it. Very elegant smell, sweet but not too sweet, very refreshing scent.

Love. Love. Love. I have been wearing this perfume for years and I get compliments all the time. I have bought others to change it up a bit but always come back to this one. It's my absolute favorite. If you've ever been in or walked past a Michael Kors store, this is the smell that floods through the store. My local store used to spray all the tissue paper that they used in the bags of merchandise. Try it out, you will not be disappointed.

amazing smell. I got a sample of this perfume while looking at a what to buy for a summer perfume. It lasts so long that I can still smell it on my skin throughout the day. it's a floral crisp clean smell and I can't get enough of it.
My new favorite. I'm so in love with this scent, it's a nice and fresh scent. Perfect for summer time!
My new favorite. I'm so in love with this scent, it's a nice and fresh scent. Perfect for summer time!

smells amazing! i absolutely love the way this smells! perfect scent for summer! i just wish i had gotten the full size bottle.

So goed that disappear in one hour! :( Nice perfume. But he scent does not last past even an hour. It's so disappointing. By the time I arrived to a party could not smell any of it.
To expensive for one hour perfume! :/
I love it! I first received this as a sample. I later purchased the smaller size and I eventually had to upgrade to the 3.4 oz. Overall it is the better buy. I love it because the smell last all day.
Amazing fragrance The fragrance is so soft and light.The smell last for 12 hours.
smells amazing! i absolutely love the way this smells! perfect scent for summer! i just wish i had gotten the full size bottle.
smells amazing! i absolutely love the way this smells! perfect scent for summer! i just wish i had gotten the full size bottle.

floral and for an older woman. I ordered this based on all the reviews but this perfume is very flowery. I was searching for the Jasmine scent. I didn't find it. It's overpowering and so I recommend only 1 or 2 sprays. A slight tinge of a peppery scent. A little goes a long way. I just ordered it to find out what the hype was all about.
Smells good. The bottle is cute and the smell is great. I always have great complements from friends when I have it on.
LOVE LOVE! Absolutely great! Item received on time with nice perfume samples. As a result of a previous order I purchase this perfume.

Tory Burch Cologne Set. I purchased this as a gift and the recipient loved it!
I want to get one for myself.

Smell of Soistication!
I absolutely love this scent! A great scent that can transition you from summer to fall/winter. It lasts all day long, with a fresh chic scent and little bit of boldness, spray more for a more intense aroma! I have received many compliments when I wear this fragrance. I highly recommend trying it!

Perfect for Summer and the Beach. I love love love this. it reminds me of sunny days, wind in my hair, sand between my toes. pure relaxation. I prefer fresh fragrances with a spike a citrus. not too florally. Def my new favorite beach in a bottle!

Disappointed. I was so excited about this new Tory Burch fragrance & couldn't wait to try it! Unfortunately, after receiving my bottle today, the first spray left me with a headache. This scent smells like men's cologne. It is overpowering. It reminds me of the original men's Polo cologne in the green bottle. Very disappointing as I love all of the other Tory Burch scents. This one will be returned.

Disappointed. I was so excited about this new Tory Burch fragrance & couldn't wait to try it! Unfortunately, after receiving my bottle today, the first spray left me with a headache. This scent smells like men's cologne. It is overpowering. It reminds me of the original men's Polo cologne in the green bottle. Very disappointing as I love all of the other Tory Burch scents. This one will be returned.
confused. it says citrus and fruity and I usually love Tory Burch which made me by it online, but this is hands down floral. will be returning tomorrow.
Love it. Great scent. Received a sample and was convinced. Lasts, compatible with me, enjoyable.

Nice scent for the Spring! I had never bought the first Tory Burch fragrance when it came out. I had other perfumes in my mind to buy like the New York Bond's No. 9 in Liberty Island. However, when Tory Burch launched her spring collection, I became curious and had to try them. I got all three in a sample set with a Sephora purchase. Jolie Fleur Bleue became an instant favorite, so I purchased it. Since then, I also fell in love with the Lavendar scent too! I really like the others too and will purchase them in the future.

Smell of Soistication!
I absolutely love this scent! A great scent that can transition you from summer to fall/winter. It lasts all day long, with a fresh chic scent and little bit of boldness, spray more for a more intense aroma! I have received many compliments when I wear this fragrance. I highly recommend trying it!
Love it. Great scent. Received a sample and was convinced. Lasts, compatible with me, enjoyable.
LOVE. I don't know why the bad reviews I absolutely love this fragrance. it's light and perfect for everyday. and very much smells like lavender and doesn't smell like old lady Like others say.
Delicious! This scent is so perfect for someone who doesn't want a super sweet or floral scent. It is just subtle enough! I wish it were a spray, but other than that it's perfect!

Meh...didn't exactly smell floral or sweet. I tried this perfume on at the Sephora store. It didn't exactly smell "floral" sprayed onto the paper or on my body. The scent was not what I was expecting and didn't work well with my body chemistry. Glad that I tried it in store because I was thinking about buying it. The bottle itself is pretty though.

Really fragrant! I actually really like this fragrance. Im a sucker for perfumes & enjoy trying different ones on to match my skin. Perfumes are soo subjective that they're difficult to review, however, I like this one so much that I decided to leave a review on it. The notes are hard to describe when someone smells me, but I can smell this perfume on me & that's what makes it great!!! Like other reviewers have stated, it lasts too, which is awesome. How many synthetic fragrances out there don't last?? I'm always looking for a scent that matches my skin/chemistry & this is IT!!!
Love the Love Not my usual floral but I love it
My new favorite and go to Love this for everyday...waited to use my 20% off because i was reluctant to buy with the high price..worth every penny! Need to grab the rollerball for my purse
The scent catches everyone for attention!!! This is my calm scent for the day.
Love! I recently had gotten a sample of this in a gift bag and it smells amazing. I decided to buy it! Usually takes me some time to purchase perfume but this was hands down awesome!
Awesome. I've received so many compliments on how good I smell. My new favorite perfume
Amazing summer scent I always always ALWAYS get compliments when I wear this perfume. Perfect for the summer months and it is more of a summery scent. Lasts all day
Absolutely obsessed with this sent. Stays on all day and always receive compliments on it.
Perfection! Love this perfume! I receive compliments every time I wear it!
